{
  "id": "adv_card_hrk_08_01",
  "title": "佐伯遙子 1話 一週間マネージャー",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_toffice_noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――遙子がサニーピースに加わる数年前",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few years ago before Haruko joining Sunny Peace",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "今日から一週間、遙子さんのマネージャーを\nすることになりました。改めてよろしくお願いします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Starting today for a week‚ I'll be Haruko-san's manager.\nNice to meet you again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.933333385,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "君はずっと麻奈ちゃんの担当だったから\n私のマネージャーなんてなんだか変な感じね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You've always been with Mana-chan‚\nso having you as my manager feels a bit odd.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.3000000517,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね。でも、やるからには精一杯務めるので\n俺にしてほしいことがあればなんでも言って下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ it does. But I'll do my best since I've taken it on.\nIf there's anything you want me to do‚ just say the word.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.5999996702,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "なんでも……？\nじゃあ、さっそくお願いしてもいいかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anything…?\nAlright then‚ can I ask you something right away?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.6666659553,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "私が{user}君にしてほしいことは……\n敬語禁止よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What I want from you‚ {user}‚ is…\nBan on honorifics.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.6666654467,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "前々から思ってたけど、君の方が年上で\n高校の先輩でもあるのに、どうしていつも敬語なの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've been thinking for a while now‚ but why do you always use honorifics\neven though you're older and my senior in high school?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.6666629035,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "それは……この業界では遙子さんの方が先輩ですから\nそれに遙子さんは年下って気がしなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… In this industry‚ you're the senior‚ Haruko-san.\nAnd it's not like I feel you're younger…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.1999962369,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "私の方が年上に見えるってこと？\nピチピチのJKを捕まえてそれは酷いんじゃないかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So you think I look older?\nIsn't it harsh to talk to fresh-faced high schooler like that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.9333290616,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ピチピチのJKですか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fresh-faced high schooler…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.3666634122,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "何その反応！\n春まで同じ高校に通ってたのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What's with that reaction!\nWe went to the same high school until spring.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.3999934394,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "す、すみません\nそうですね、遙子さんはピチピチのJKです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-Sorry.\nRight‚ Haruko-san is a fresh-faced high schooler.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.4999934394,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "……はぁ。こういうやり取りをしちゃうから\n{user}君の敬語が抜けないのかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Sigh. Maybe these kinds of exchanges are\nwhy you can't drop the honorifics‚ {user}.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.9999924222,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "気心が知れてるのも考えものだわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Understanding each other can be complicated…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.6999924222,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.0166590888
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.0166590888
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、遙子さんの担任は高橋先生なんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ Haruko's homeroom teacher is Takahashi-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.0666590888,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "そうだけど……高橋先生のこと知ってるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah right… Do you know Takahashi-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.0999924222,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.1999924222
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "俺が一年生の時に副担任だったんです\n口癖が面白くて、クラスの男子がよく真似してたなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ he was my co-teacher when I was in 10th grade.\nHis catchphrase was funny‚ and the boys in class often imitated him.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.5999924222,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "そうそう、話し方に特徴があるのよね\nうちのクラスでも真似してる子がいたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right‚ he had a distinctive way of speaking.\nThere were kids in our class who imitated him too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.9333227037,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 112.0333206692
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、音楽の林先生は知ってる？\n麻奈ちゃんと仲が良かったらしいんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How about Hayashi-san‚ the music teacher?\nHe seemed close to Mana-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.2333206692,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん覚えてます！　娘さんがアイドル好きで\nこっそり麻奈のサインをもらってましたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ I remember! His daughter is an idol fan‚\nso she secretly got Mana's autograph.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.8999873358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.6666540025
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、そうなの？　私もよく話すけど\n一度もサインを頼まれたことないわよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really? Even though we talk a lot‚\nhe never asked me for an autograph.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.5333206692,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.7333196519
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "それはきっと……いえ、なんでもないです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's probably because… No‚ it's nothing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.7333196519,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "{user}君、今失礼なこと考えたでしょ\nどうせ私は人気がないわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-kun‚ you thought of something rude just now‚ didn't you?\nAnyway‚ you probably think I'm not that popular.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.5666346746,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 145.9999853012
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01-hrk014.m4a",
      "text": "……ふふ、やっぱり君は話しやすくていいわね\n三枝さんも穏やかで話しやすいけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Haha‚ I like that you're easy to talk to.\nSaegusa-san is easygoing too‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.7333186345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 150.7333186345
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01-hrk015.m4a",
      "text": "業界の大先輩で歳の差もあるから\nなかなかざっくばらんにとはいかないのよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's hard to be so casual with someone who's a senior\nin the industry and much older.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.2666529851,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 160.4999863185
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01-hrk016.m4a",
      "text": "その点、君なら歳も近いし共通の話題も多いから\n肩の力を抜いて話せるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But with you‚ we're close in age and have a lot of common ground‚\nso we can relax and chat.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.2666529851,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 167.9333186345
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01-hrk017.m4a",
      "text": "{user}君なら、私のマネージャーを\nずっと続けてくれてもいいんだけどなー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If only you could stay as\nmy manager forever‚ {user}.",
